ComicInfo.Series: Legends of Oz: Tik-Tok and the Kalidah
ComicInfo.Summary:
Tik Tok makes his triumphant debut in this all-new spin-off Legend of Oz: The Wicked West adventure! The quest for the most powerful relic in Oz continues in this thrilling second chapter by newcomers Keith Thomas and Renato Rei!
Featuring an all original story, don't miss out on Aspen's newest BDI launch title with the LEGENDS OF OZ: TIK TOK AND THE KALIDAH #2!
